{"tid":2489581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"攜2支玩具槍訪警察學院開放日　21歲港台兼職記者被捕","createTime":"2021-04-15T04:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:28:42.000Z","uid":44209,"like":49,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"d51b153757c378e9f0c2aa4b7652e844c2a6f385","tid":2489581,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃竹坑香港警察學院今日(15日)舉辦開放日，據了解，早上8時許、即開放日開始之前，警方在學院附近一帶巡邏，期間在港鐵海洋公園站截停1名21歲男子，竟在其背囊發現2支玩具槍及2部對講機。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，以涉嫌藏有仿製槍械拘捕他，帶署扣查。有消息指，被捕的男子為IVE學生，為港台兼職記者，今日擬到警察學院採訪，又聲稱該些玩具槍是昨日拍攝微電影所用，未及收拾。"},{"pid":"0e3b69afca85a7325160bb6af467d6c391bc6d5a","tid":2489581,"uid":30084,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"等睇記協出聲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63f43897a58b0cc3e4ca4ede4ffceafe77d778c","tid":2489581,"uid":202511,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:41:51.000Z","msg":"仿製槍械比賣唔比帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43f4e47a6c8b2b10ac25da5155caf090b389d5e","tid":2489581,"uid":31296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"捕風捉影"},{"pid":"56010609a297f236135dd4ae094bab917adc85f4","tid":2489581,"uid":157073,"like":64,"dislike":3,"score":61,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"咁去打wargame咪全部拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f2b498f0ebaa715343fdc7042d6ecf6a873509","tid":2489581,"uid":51271,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTi